High school football fans, Friday night is your time to shine on WUSA9! 
Our sports team has narrowed the Friday night football field down to four fantastic matchups. The winner...chosen by YOU...will be crowned our GAME ON Varsity Game of the Week this Thursday night at 8pm when the poll closes. 
That means interviews, highlights, and so much more. So tell friends, family and fellow football fanatics to get clicking!
